---
title: Saucy BBQ Double Beef Meatballs with Mashed Potatoes and Garlicky Broccoli
description: These tasty meatballs are flavoured with BBQ spices, chives and garlic, then tossed in a savoury-sweet BBQ sauce. This dish is a comfort food classic, great for any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-double-boeuf-bbq-4670e1af.jpg
